perl-http-daemon (A simple http server class)

HTTP::Daemon - A simple http server class
Instances of the HTTP::Daemon class are HTTP/1.1 servers that listen
on a socket for incoming requests. The HTTP::Daemon is a subclass of
IO::Socket::IP, so you can perform socket operations directly on it
too.

HOME: https://github.com/libwww-perl/HTTP-Daemon

======================================================================
REQUIRES: perl-http-date perl-http-message perl-lwp-mediatypes perl-module-build 

